data.description: Inquire about existing assumable mortgage at 4%. Exquisite executive home just minutes from Lake Lanier Experience the pinnacle of luxurious living in the breathtaking transformation of this executive home, perfectly situated just moments from the serene shores of Lake Lanier. If you're a boating enthusiast, the convenience of docking your boat at Habersham Marina, a mere mile away, awaits you. With its lavish interior and extensive upgrades, this residence is the embodiment of modern elegance. Key Features: Gleaming Hardwood Floors: Beautifully refinished hardwood floors add timeless charm and sophistication to the living spaces. Renovations Galore: Enjoy peace of mind with many upgrades, freshly painted exteriors and interiors, brand-new lighting, and plumbing fixtures that infuse contemporary style throughout. Smart Home Innovations: The addition of smart home lighting fixtures not only enhances convenience but also underscores the home's commitment to modern living. Elegant Living Areas: The family room, crowned with a fireplace, offers a cozy retreat, while the main-level office provides a dedicated workspace. Opulent Master Suite: The spacious master suite features trey ceilings and a wall of windows, immersing the room in natural light. The ensuite spa bathroom has been lavishly upgraded with new tile, a frameless shower door, new countertops, plumbing fixtures, and lighting. Generous Bedrooms: All bedrooms feature walk-in closets, providing ample storage space for all your needs. Investment Potential: This property offers endless possibilities with no rental restrictions, making it ideal for a luxurious short-term rental or executive rental. Top-Notch Schools: Enjoy the benefits of residing in the highly-rated Forsyth County school district, ensuring an exceptional education for your family. $100K in Renovations: Witness the incredible transformation of this home, both inside and out, with a substantial investment of $100,000 in upgrades and enhancements. Three-Car Garage: The spacious three-car garage effortlessly accommodates your vehicles and storage requirements. Modern Kitchen: The remodeled kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring exquisite countertops and stainless steel appliances. A separate dining room adds a touch of elegance to your dining experiences. Outdoor Paradise: Step onto the expansive deck and relish the privacy of the park-like backyard, which offers ample space for a future pool, in-ground firepit, or children's playground. Additional Highlights: Notable features such as the grand two-story foyer, striking wagon wheel chandelier, LED lighting throughout, a cozy fireplace, a new downstairs HVAC system, and professional landscaping contribute to the overall appeal. Terrace Level Bonus: Discover a fabulous man cave with a city loft vibe on the terrace level, providing a perfect space for entertaining and relaxation. This executive home is the epitome of refined living, blending the allure of a top-tier residence with contemporary updates and an enviable location near Lake Lanier. Seize this opportunity to make this your dream home. Listing agent is related to Seller. Inquire about existing assumable mortgage at 4%.
